| current_awards = 
| image          = Euronyr12105200255 widec.jpg
| imagesize      = 200px
| alt            = A black circle with an octagonal silver plaque in the middle. The edge of the plaque reads &quot;KENESAW MOUNTAIN LANDIS AWARD BASEBALL MEMORIAL&quot;. In the middle of the octagon is a baseball diamond which contains, from the top, a man's face in gold, &quot;Most Valuable Player&quot;, the winner's league, his name in a gold rectangle, and his team.
