==Notes==
*{{note label|Number|a|a}} A player is considered inactive if he has announced his retirement or not played for a full season.
*{{note label|Number|b|b}} A unanimous victory indicates that the player received all possible first-place votes.
*{{note label|Number|c|c}} Hernandez and Stargell both received 216&amp;nbsp;points in the 1979 voting.&lt;ref name=&quot;1979 awards&quot; /&gt;

